        <h3 style="margin-top: 0px;" id="pop_facts">
            Hopkinsville Population Facts
        </h3>
    


            <h4>What is the current population of Hopkinsville?</h4>
            <p>
                Based on the latest 2022 data from the US census, the
                current population of Hopkinsville is 30,683.  Hopkinsville, Kentucky is the 1,287th largest city in the US.
            </p>

            
                <h4>What county is Hopkinsville, Kentucky in?</h4>
                <p>
                
                    Hopkinsville is located entirely in 
                    Christian County.
                
                </p>
            

            
                
                    <h4>What is the size of Hopkinsville, Kentucky in square miles?</h4>
                    Hopkinsville has an area of 
                    30.7 square miles.

                    
                    
                        Hopkinsville is the
                        
                            4th
                        
                        largest city, by area, in Kentucky.
                    
                
            

            <h4>What was the peak population of Hopkinsville?</h4>
            <p>
                
                    The peak population of Hopkinsville was in
                    2010, when its population was
                    31,577.
                    
                        In 2010, Hopkinsville was the
                        1,135th largest city in the US; now
                        its fallen to the 1,287th largest city in
                        the US.
                    
                    Hopkinsville is currently
                        <span style="color: red;">
                            2.8%
                            smaller
                        </span>
                        than it was in 2010.
                    </p>
                
            </p>
            
                
                    <h4>How quickly is Hopkinsville growing?</h4>
                
                <p>
                    
                        Hopkinsville has grown
                        1.6% 
                        since the 2000.
                    


                    
                        Hopkinsville, Kentucky's growth is below average.
                        72% of similarly sized
                        cities are growing faster since 2000.
                    
                </p>
            

            

            
                <h4>What is the population density of Hopkinsville, Kentucky?</h4>
                <p>
                Hopkinsville has a population density of
                1,029.8 people
                per square mile.

                
                
                </p>
            

            

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
